  <brief_title>Comparison of Skin Adhesive to Subcuticular Suture Wound Closure After Port Placement</brief_title>
  <acronym>PWC</acronym>
  <official_title>Open, Randomized, Controlled Non-inferiority Trial to Compare Synthetic Tissue Adhesive and Skin Suture After Port Catheter Implantation With Reference to Cosmetic Result and Economy of Time at Equal Risk for Wound Infection</official_title>
